comment: Exum (UTA) and Dedmon (SAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Mack (UTA) makes contact with the ball and the part of Dedmon's (SAS) hand that is considered part of the ball.
Bertans (SAS) and Lyles (UTA) briefly engage and separate.
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with Withey (UTA) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Dedmon (SAS) makes marginal contact with Withey (UTA) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Lyles (UTA) allows Bertans (SAS) to land following the jump shot attempt.
Bertans (SAS) is in a legal guarding position and deflects the ball away from Lyles (UTA).
Anderson (SAS) makes body to body contact with Burks (UTA) that affects his SQBR.
Exum (UTA) and Murray (SAS) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Murray (SAS) makes body to body contact with Mack (UTA) that affects his SQBR.
Withey (UTA) makes incidental contact with Dedmon (SAS) during rebounding.
Dedmon (SAS) clamps Withey's (UTA) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
